snippet.title: Swindler The Game 1.0: Ready for Launch!
snippet.description: The first glimpse at the gameplay of Swindler, which, by the way, is uploaded to the OUYA store as of tonight! Here is a play through of one brief session, filmed in real time. Try and beat that score! For more information on Swindler, visit swindlerthegame.com.
